  {charity_id: 446, charity_number: "SC001071", charity_name: "Solas Scotland Ltd (subject to insolvency proceedings)", registered_date: "04/03/1987 00:00", known_as: "Solas Scotland", charity_status: "Not Monitored", postcode: "G82 2DL", constitutional_form: "Company (the charity is registered with Companies House)", previous_constitutional_form_1: "", geographical_spread: "More than one local authority area in Scotland", main_operating_location: "West Dunbartonshire", purposes: "'The prevention or relief of poverty','The advancement of environmental protection or improvement'", beneficiaries: "'No specific group, or for the benefit of the community'", activities: "'It carries out activities or services itself'", objectives: "(a) (i) To provide relief from the problems of poverty caused by the effects of cold, badly insulated and draughty houses and shortage of money to meet fuel costs.\r\r(ii) To provide information, advice and education in the field of insulation, draughtproofing, energy conservation and heating problems. (iii) To provide training and support to encourage the participation  of residents of Dunbarton and environs in projects to alleviate the problems associated with fuel poverty. (iv) To relieve poverty through: (a) the promotion of companies whose activities are directed towards the provision of paid employment to people who are in a state of poverty or towards relief from need among people who are in a state of poverty, the acquisition and holding of shares, stocks, debentures and other interests in companies whose activities are so directed and the provision of managerial, supervisory and consultancy services to or in respect of such companies (b) the provision of advice and assistance with regard to the establishment and operation of enterprises whose activities are directed towards the aims referred to in sub-paragraph (a) (c) the promotion and implementation of schemes of community benefit of a charitable nature within Dunbarton and environs